OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and breezy across much of
OL,6,Fthe region, although some light rain
OL,7,Fpossible across the Pennines during
OL,8,Fthe morning. Plenty of sunny spells,
OL,9,Fespecially through the afternoon.
OL,10,FTemperatures around average.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA pleasant evening with
OL,13,Fwidespread sunshine and easing winds
OL,14,Ffor many, followed by a mostly clear
OL,15,Fnight. Remaining breezy along coasts.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FCloudy through the morning on
OL,18,FFriday, some sunny spells through the
OL,19,Fafternoon. Cloudier again into the
OL,20,Fevening with the possibility of some
OL,21,Flight rain in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
